 	compression-aware; don't duplicate the work.

	* prim/packages.el (packages-hardcoded-lisp): Remove "cl-defs".

	* custom/wid-edit.el: Use `remove-if'.
	(widget-glyph-directory): Use `locate-data-directory'.

